{
  "texts": [
    "A public blockchain is developed for the proposed scheme.",
    "A new block that contains the hash value, the descriptive summary, and the encrypted storage list is created on the blockchain.",
    "The block also contains the block id, p id, timestamp and previous block hash.",
    "Algorithm I presents the pseudo-code of the Data Saving Phase of the proposed scheme.",
    "Algorithm 1 EMR Data SavingIn the proposed scheme, AES-256 is used as the symmetric encryption algorithm, Elliptic Curve (EC-secp112r1) is used as the asymmetric encryption algorithm, and SHA-256 is used as the hash function."
  ]
}